Modified mix of propietary libraries provided by the manufacturer for encoding
using Amlogic Video Engine hardware. 

AVE hardware encoding must be mainlined into Linux kernel as a V4L2 driver.


Amlogic Video Engine (AVE) Encoding
===================================

Maximum resolution
------------------
Encoder width and heigh resolution limitation: HD definition (1920Ã—1080).
The encoder is limited by width and heigh not the amount of pixels or memory
used by each frame.


Supported pixel formats
-----------------------

YUV 4:2:0
 * I420
 * NV12
 * NV21
